Package model.metaheuristic.experiment.component

A package with the implementation of ExperimentComponent

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComputeQualityIndicators<S extends Solution<?>>
    This class computes the QualityIndicators of an experiment.
    GenerateFriedmanHolmTestTables
    This class computes the Friedman test ranking and generates a Latex script that produces a table per quality indicator containing the ranking and the result of the Holm post hoc test.
    GenerateFriedmanTestTables
    This class computes the Friedman test ranking and generates a Latex script that produces a table per quality indicator containing the ranking The results are a set of Latex files that are written in the directory #getExperimentBaseDirectory()/latex.
    GenerateHtmlPages
    This class executes a StudyVisualizer on the experiment provided.
    GenerateLatexTablesWithStatistics
    This class computes a number of statistical values (mean, median, standard deviation, interquartile range) from the indicator files generated after executing ExecutionIndicatorTask and ComputeQualityIndicators.
    GenerateReferenceParetoFrontInDisk
    This class computes a reference Pareto front from a set of files.
    GenerateReferenceParetoFrontInRAM
    This class computes a reference Pareto front from a set of files.
    GenerateWilcoxonTestTablesWithR
    This class generates a R script that computes the Wilcoxon Signed Rank Test and generates a Latex script that produces a table per quality indicator containing the pairwise comparison between all the algorithms on all the solved problems.
    ObjectSolution
    Solution used to wrap any type of decision variable.
